when you think you have it as clean as you can

00:03:16.870 --> 00:03:19.890
turn it all on high again

00:03:19.890 --> 00:03:23.020
hit your igniter

00:03:23.020 --> 00:03:28.320
and close the lid

00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:35.320
and let it all cook for another 15
minutes

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:39.740
a tip I learned a couple years ago your
igniter

00:03:39.750 --> 00:03:43.989
