pulled out the battery and stuck in

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:54.290
a new one so check yours  out if you
think

00:03:54.290 --> 00:03:57.650
your barbecue doesn't light for some
reason in case that's your problem

00:03:57.650 --> 00:04:02.019
I don't think I'm the only person
didn't know that but you just never know

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:11.690
heat it up 15 minutes before you use it

00:04:11.690 --> 00:04:14.850
give it a good scrub down with your brush anytime you are going to use it

00:04:14.850 --> 00:04:18.210
then season your grill

00:04:18.210 --> 00:04:22.039
take an oily paper towel

00:04:22.039 --> 00:04:26.190
rub it across your grill

00:04:26.190 --> 00:04:30.289
if it flares up hit it with a water bottle to take any bottle fill it with water

00:04:30.289 --> 00:04:35.400
